<subSubSection pageId="84" pageNumber="842" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="84.[1447,2656,1227,2281]" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1448,1583,1814,1847]" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">Breeding.</emphasis>
A lactating Thomas’s Big-eared Brown Bat was caught in November in 
<collectingCountry name="Argentina" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">Argentina</collectingCountry>
